All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Day
    Represents a single Day in the year
    EventLog
    Creates a cumulative log of all actions performed during each session
    GoogleProcessing
    Handles all IO operations between AGILE Planner and Google Calendar
    GoogleUtil
    Handler of all core linker and utility functions for GoogleIO
    IOProcessing
    Handles all input/output functionality for the ScheduleManager
    ScheduleManager
    Handles the generation and management of the overall schedule
    SimpleUI
    Basic Command Line UI
    SystemManager
    Primary controller for all the interacting parts of AGILE Planner
    Task
    The core element of the underlying schedule.
    Task.CheckList
    CheckList for each individual task assigned to a day
    Task.CheckList.Item
    Represents a single Item in a CheckList
    Task.SubTask
    The individual component of a parent Task in the form of a SubTask TODO will need to include a markComplete() method
    Time
    Handles all time operations involving Calendar instances
    UserConfig
    Handles the management of all user config settings and data
